txt.en: 'An Uruk known as Shatúrro has been hired by those across the bridge. Shatúrro brings a large group of hunters with him. You should help me take care of this, as I do not have the time. Make haste!'
'The hunters of Shatúrro are all gone you say? Hahaha!'
Shatúrro's hunters can be found in Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should defeat any hunters under the command of Shatúrro.
The Khundolar Commander can be found at Fushaum Bal North.\n\nYou should talk to the Khundolar Commander.
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
